OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FBritain is set to announce extra
OL,7,Fsupport for Ukraine, worth millions of
OL,8,Fpounds, as senior ministers hold a
OL,9,Fseries of meetings with their
OL,10,Finternational counterparts.
OL,12,FIn Washington DC on Wednesday,
OL,13,FChancellor Rachel Reeves is expected
OL,14,Fto confirm a #752 million payment to
OL,15,FKyiv ahead of a meeting with Ukrainian
OL,16,FPrime Minister Yulia Svyrydenko.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FThe payment, part of a #3.36 billion
OL,7,Floan, is intended to help pay for
OL,8,Fweaponry including long-range
OL,9,Fmissiles, air defence systems and
OL,10,Fdrones.
OL,12,FReeves said: "This funding will help
OL,13,Fdeliver the military equipment Ukraine
OL,14,Fneeds as it defends itself against
OL,15,FRussia's unprovoked war.
OL,17,F"I am proud that the UK is a leading
OL,18,Fpartner in providing vital support to
OL,19,FUkraine, and we will continue to step
OL,20,Fup to do more while keeping pressure
OL,21,Fon Russia."
OL,26,@tD@NOUyD@AOU}D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
