FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Defence Secretary John
OL,7,FHealey will use a meeting of the
OL,8,FUkraine Defence Contact Group (UDCG)
OL,9,Fto announce the UK's biggest ever
OL,10,Fdrone package for Ukraine that will
OL,11,Fsee 120,000 drones delivered to the
OL,12,Fcountry.
OL,14,FThe package will include long-range
OL,15,Fstrike drones, reconnaissance drones,
OL,16,Flogistics drones and those with
OL,17,Fmaritime capabilities, with many
OL,18,Fproduced by UK-based companies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FHealey said: "This big boost of battle-
OL,7,Fproven drones will give Ukrainian
OL,8,Fforces the capability they need to
OL,9,Fdefend their people and fight back
OL,10,Fagainst Russian aggression."
OL,12,FDrones have increasingly come to
OL,13,Fdominate the war in Ukraine, with the
OL,14,Ftechnology now responsible for the
OL,15,Fmajority of battlefield casualties.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,26,@nD@NOUrD@\O]
