FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FOn Monday, Ukrainian President
OL,7,FVolodymyr Zelensky said Ukraine had
OL,8,Fcaptured a Russian position using
OL,9,Fground-based and aerial drones alone
OL,10,Ffor the first time.
OL,12,FHealey also urged the public not to be
OL,13,F"distracted" from Ukraine by the war
OL,14,Fin the Middle East, adding: "Nothing
OL,15,Fwill distract us from continuing to
OL,16,Fstand with them for as long as it
OL,17,Ftakes to secure peace."
OL,26,@uD@AOUuD@LO]vD@]OUyD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
