FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1776276668
OL,3,CUK to send #752 million and 120,000
OL,4,Cdrones to Ukraine
OL,6,FThe Defence Secretary will make the
OL,7,Fannouncement as he chairs the UDCG in
OL,8,FBerlin alongside his German and
OL,9,FUkrainian counterparts and Nato
OL,10,Fsecretary general Mark Rutte.
OL,12,FThe 50-strong group brings together
OL,13,FUkraine's allies for regular meetings,
OL,14,Fand was chaired by the United States
OL,15,Funtil Donald Trump's return to the
OL,16,FWhite House last year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
